, they ought to beware as, lacking the attention of a trained fletcher, improvised arrows are prone to fumbling.</p>\n<table style=\"width:100.998%;height:378.375px\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:36.375px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:37.8218%;height:36.375px\">\n<p><strong>Weapon</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.2772%;text-align:center;height:36.375px\">\n<p><strong>Price</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.31683%;text-align:center;height:36.375px\">\n<p><strong>Enc</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:15.4455%;text-align:center;height:36.375px\">\n<p><strong>Availability</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.6733%;text-align:center;height:36.375px\">\n<p><strong>Range</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.2673%;text-align:center;height:36.375px\">\n<p><strong>Damage</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:21px\">\n<td style=\"font-family:CaslonAntique;font-weight:bold;width:99.802%;height:21px;text-align:center\" colspan=\"6\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;font-family:CaslonAntique;font-size:var(--font-size-18);margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:CaslonAntique\"><strong>BOW</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:31px\">\n<td style=\"width:37.8218%;height:31px;text-align:center\">\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.trappings.6GNNpWIGxO9CkTCR]{Arrow (12)}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.2772%;text-align:center;height:31px\">5/–</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.31683%;text-align:center;height:31px\">0</td>\n<td style=\"width:15.4455%;text-align:center;height:31px\">Common</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.6733%;text-align:center;height:31px\">As weapon</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.2673%;text-align:center;height:31px\">–</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:31px\">\n<td style=\"width:37.8218%;height:31px;text-align:center\">\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-up-in-arms.items.aR4Yg3dEL5FdEW0q]{Barbed Arrow (12)}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.2772%;text-align:center;height:31px\">/–</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.31683%;text-a