-core.skills.7ToyUcqJDkceoJRd]{Lore (Science)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Guilder)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.r180vP86SlwyJc8W]{Criminal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.epPBu7x6BRWp2PHG]{Dealmaker}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Guilder)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.G4rPR0XGiYFUZWKi]{Pharmacist}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Guild License, Trade Tools<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.oA7LO3muxy9LNEJD]{Master Apothecary}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9tbHTeuvEMZrp0rx]{Research}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.D4JNPSl6VOpsVmSi]{Secret Signs (Guilder)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.zv3IyoU2wkPZu8pD]{Bookish}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GHmXS9zGNx3PWYZc]{Master Tradesman (Apothecary)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.vMYEkrWj0ip6ZOdv]{Resistance (Poison)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QsrXxGZiHjth7RMg]{Savvy}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Book (Apothecary), Apprentice, Workshop<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.y0V0xRFindJiBUDz]{Apothecary-General}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oSbEE6eXH1S3LfUU]{Ride (Horse)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.9h82z72XGo9tfgQS]{Acute Sense (Taste)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.JLzJws09GMw9GWBV]{Coolheaded}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GHmXS9zGNx3PWYZc]{Master Tradesman (Poisoner)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.580fwhKfOZJFxMID]{Savant (Apothecary)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Commission Papers, Large Workshop<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"86gkaanqt19xYCRa","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":500000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Priest","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><p>‘For sound advice, I seek a Priest of Verena. For everything else, I seek a Priest of Ranald.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Wermer Losch, Merchant</em></p><p>‘The Shallyan, just a girl she was, stroked my little Anton’s forehead and whispered, and the screaming stopped. He smiled at me for the first time in days. I will never forget it. Oh, aye, he died not long after, but not in pain. Not in pain.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Sabine Schmidt, Fishmonger</em></p><p>‘Listen, there is nothing to fear. Hexensnacht comes every year. We need only call on the Lord of Death to watch over us. So, come the midnight hour, we cry MORR! MORR! MORR!’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Father Wilhelm Abgott, Priest of Morr</em></p></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You carry the word of your god, tending to the spiritual needs of the masses.</em></p><p>Priests tend to congregations of the faithful throughout the Old World. While many are assigned to a specific temple, others choose a wandering life to reach worshippers who cannot, or will not, attend temple. They are expected to exemplify the beliefs of their religion — which vary greatly depending on which deity they serve. High Priests are responsible for a temple and all its Cult and lay members. Alongside Lectors, they will often be called upon to advise the ruling classes, with many active in local politics. Priests have many duties connected to their God, such as Priests of Manann’s responsibility to consecrate new ships, or a Shallyan’s duty to tend to the sick and wounded, so they touch on most aspects of life in the Empire. For more on religion and the different Orders, see Chapter 7: Religion and Belief.</p><p>Some temple-bound Priests seek distractions to justify sojourns away. Disturbing matters heard from their congregations can send them on a quest for answers. Some High Priests find their administrative duties so far removed from the life they envisaged when they joined the Cult that they take extended pilgrimages away from their temple.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/priest.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Academics</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Priest Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.u2DMz1B0DyUHBi6Z]{Initiate}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d9bGxy6Y3u3rOHIN]{Lore (Theology)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9xR9uO8FIvi4YsJp]{Pray}</em>, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9tbHTeuvEMZrp0rx]{Research}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-akoris.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-akoris.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QyjWtSdnVMT04l5Y]{Bless (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Nj3tC8A5fZ3zEdMR]{Holy Visions}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GogGbYxkVdCmiKqf]{Read/Write}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.LPgjE0cexTVOBVCY]{Suave}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Religious Symbol, Robes<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.AtWEBwIobFnhbQy7]{Priest}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.qBm2fu3oMhxsDBNQ]{Entertain (Storytelling)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.HXZaV1CJhmTvcAz4]{Heal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.rOPmyLWa37e7s9v6]{Melee (Basic)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.77p3QRKgFWakkndF]{Blather}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.zv3IyoU2wkPZu8pD]{Bookish}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Cultists)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.voV0C2ar1bKpcpnH]{Invoke (Any)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Book (Religion), Ceremonial Robes<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.lfRarot8alDa1WjG]{High Priest}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.fdq3RFSOKl5b3WzW]{Art (Writing)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.0CwV96kTDRF0jUhk]{Entertain (Speeches)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DiP9cmbqUir3HkkK]{Lore (Heraldry)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.9h82z72XGo9tfgQS]{Acute Sense (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.E98mVLZgE8bX5vQW]{Hatred (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.oGbDwnLOn3isPJpO]{Impassioned Zeal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Ywo6fZNPC4zbHHSQ]{Strong-minded}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Quality Robes, Religious Relic, Subordinate Priests, Temple<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.UptqmlN6znCIOxNW]{Lector}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Politics)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.ZWcTbeK8i9vKph2a]{Master Orator}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wNvPXAhlKABl6hpk]{Pure Soul}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.vMYEkrWj0ip6ZOdv]{Resistance (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.580fwhKfOZJFxMID]{Savant (Theology)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Library (Theology), Subordinate High Priests<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"h1l9jvaIxsb92wtM","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":5600000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Lawyer","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>‘Sharks! No, worse! Leeches! But not the good kind that suck out bad humors, oh no. They’re leeches that drain your coffers and leave you nothing to show for it.’ – Stefan Bachler, Merchant ‘It is not what the lawyer says I may do that concerns me, but what is right by reason and justice. Such matters need then be the basis of our new law.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Lector @UUID[JournalEntry.ozE2DMCMK64eE5pD.JournalEntryPage.sVFygKRicWFw6BsT#sample-reikland-estate]{Agatha von Böhrn}, Supreme Law Lord of the Empire</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You navigate treacherous legal systems, defending clients and prosecuting the guilty.</em></p><p>Lawyers give legal counsel, interpret the law, and argue on behalf of their clients before the courts. They are often specialists in the laws of the province in which they practice, or in ecclesiastical law. Most are university educated and therefore rich and well-connected, although gifted individuals of low birth are sometimes apprenticed. Cult lawyers learn from their venerable peers, with those trained by the Cults of Verena and Sigmar especially well-regarded. Some Lawyers are hired as mediators, settling informal disputes outside costly courts, a practice favored by Halﬂings. Others work for criminal gangs, exploiting legal loopholes to free their always-guilty clients. At the top end of society, Barristers are the only lawyers allowed to address higher appeal courts in the city-states, charging exorbitant prices for their services.</p><p>Lawyers excel at getting people out of trouble, while adventurers excel at getting into it. They can use their knowledge of obscure local laws to avoid problems by suggesting unusual approaches to solve thorny dilemmas. After all, tying up a local thug in court is just as valuable, and arguably much safer, than tying one up in a basement.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/lawyer.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling, High Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Academics</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Lawyer Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.ZSet34kUw1Bu1PDx]{Student Lawyer}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e