 2 Sets of Clothing, Deck of Cards, Dice<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.HoIgGN5ORog5dkIl]{Charlatan}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.0CwV96kTDRF0jUhk]{Entertain (Acting)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bSWoV1IiS5qWNw39]{Evaluate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.77p3QRKgFWakkndF]{Blather}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.r180vP86SlwyJc8W]{Criminal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.9sMAf0xmehjEmUao]{Fast Hands}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.PJ4oxDExnuFNr2Fi]{Secret Identity}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: 1 Forged Document, 2 Sets of Quality Clothing, Selection of Colored Powders and Water, Selection of Trinkets and Charms<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.RdnDGTwpYFhCID6N]{Con Artist}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Thief )}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DiP9cmbqUir3HkkK]{Lore (Heraldry)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.AkjRsazdAppqveZu]{Pick Lock}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bVdhLdfuSAfMi3qq]{Secret Signs (Thief )}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.6l3jvIAvrKxt0lA9]{Attractive}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.LzgxyMknSHjSkkeQ]{Cat-tongued}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.epPBu7x6BRWp2PHG]{Dealmaker}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GogGbYxkVdCmiKqf]{Read/Write}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Disguise Kit, Lock Picks, Multiple Forged Documents<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.yRRDOZ82C4ZLR6ju]{Scoundrel}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Genealogy)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9tbHTeuvEMZrp0rx]{Research}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.8lSoPDGrmeTIaapm]{Gregarious}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.WoXShzaYkV5F6c48]{Master of Disguise}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.AcnFuDKRemLI9ey7]{Nose for Trouble}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.LPgjE0cexTVOBVCY]{Suave}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Forged Seal, Writing Kit<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"Eg5D2UI3U4SAHnuU","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":1900000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Warrior Priest","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>‘Surrounded, we were, Greenskins on all sides. They knew we were done. Then the priest raises his hammer towards the sky and bellows his prayer. And as the words echoed to silence, the lightning struck. And we were all unharmed, I swear to Sigmar. But the Goblins? All dead.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Holger Kass, 1st Bögenhafen Halberdiers</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You bring divinity to the thick of battle, slaying the enemies of the Empire with righteous fury</em></p><p>Some cults of the Empire have clerics trained for war. In the Reikland, the Warrior Priests of Sigmar are the most common example of this, and most armies of the Empire are accompanied by hammer-bearing priests encouraging the soldiers in the name of Sigmar. But other cults, especially those of Myrmidia, Ulric, Taal, and Morr, have Warrior Priests of their own, each with their unique views as to how war should be conducted. Away from the battlefield, Warrior Priests are also expected to administer to soldiers’ spiritual wellbeing, as well as making sure morale stays high and discipline is ordered. Some orders of Warrior Priests swear oaths to roam the Empire, seeking heresy wherever it lies, helping where they can. Others prefer not to join armies, but lead them…</p><p>While many Warrior Priests stay with the army, some serve their cult in missionary work, and others wander the Empire as they will. As such, Warrior Priests can be natural adventurers. Of course, to pursue leads to the ends of the Empire they might require the permission of their cult, and perhaps their commanders.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/warrior-priest.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Warrior</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\">Warrior Priest Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.OERQpwcRziRTeQRb]{Novitiate (Warrior Priest)}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.HXZaV1CJhmTvcAz4]{Heal}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}</em>, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d9bGxy6Y3u3rOHIN]{Lore (Theology)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.F8NfBZdVSEIGCMtu]{Melee (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9xR9uO8FIvi4YsJp]{Pray}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QyjWtSdnVMT04l5Y]{Bless (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Cultists)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GogGbYxkVdCmiKqf]{Read/Write}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Ywo6fZNPC4zbHHSQ]{Strong-minded}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Book (Religion), Leather Jerkin, Religious Symbol, Robes, Weapon (Any Melee)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.y8XGpUCRkxdnn0ys]{Warrior Priest}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.0CwV96kTDRF0jUhk]{Entertain (Speeches)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (battle)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.F8NfBZdVSEIGCMtu]{Melee (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Z9hQe46ykQBZneoU]{Ranged (Any)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.URwIDtInCsxOoGqM]{Dual Wielder}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.WCXnFSV4WOSmzzc4]{Inspiring}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.voV0C2ar1bKpcpnH]{Invoke (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jQmIu8P85tF0njmD]{Seasoned Traveller}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Breastplate, Weapon (Any)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.6D6FQRqfc6F3L5vZ]{Priest Sergeant}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.MXy22hFCgntdlQrn]{Animal Care}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oSbEE6eXH1S3LfUU]{Ride (Horse)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.0LdHytqyNmg2pcAX]{Combat Aware}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Nj3tC8A5fZ3zEdMR]{Holy Visions}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wNvPXAhlKABl6hpk]{Pure Soul}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.IogM5gnsoOX63w7j]{Stout-hearted}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Light Warhorse with Saddle and Tack<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.20R2NFpiGkiyhwdE]{Priest Captain}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.R2ytluHiEFF2KQ5e]{Consume Alcohol}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Warfare)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.8pVzgPkgWpTJvfhG]{Fearless (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.BlHVzfs0Ow6IYEDw]{Furious Assault}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.RyxOZqcBNZ7Zw721]{Holy Hatred}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.vCgEAetBMngR53aT]{War Leader}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Religious Relic<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"iYVpqJ6bz8fokdmf","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":7800000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Huffer","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>A great big ship came in from Marienburg, low in the water and packed to the gunwales. I said that it would cost them a crown to take them through the Furdienst. Steep, yes, but it was a big ship. The arrogant Wastelander scoffed, said he’d do it himself. But sure enough, they drifted right into the shallows and were holed. They lost a good part of their cargo and it took them a week to repair the damage. Reckon it cost them a bit more than a crown.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Ilsa Dasche, Huffer</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You pilot ships and boats through the most treacherous waters of the Old World</em></p><p>Huffers are specialist river guides with expert knowledge of local river systems. They are a common sight near the most dangerous stretches of the Empire’s rivers and can command significant wages for what many view as easy work. Others view it as cheap compared to the potential cost of lost cargo.</p><p>Many Huffers specialize in a single, notorious stretch of water, while others make their money at certain times of the year when the waters are at their worst. Other Huffers have broader knowledge and will guide vessels for their entire journey, effectively acting as navigators. This is especially true of merchant ships with particularly valuable cargo at difficult times of the year.</p><p>As an expert for hire, Huffers are often hired by wealthy patrons, frequently brought in as specialists on journeys of discovery. Even when travelling into the unknown, Huffers are useful for their broad range of knowledge concerning river conditions and piloting. Because of the regional and seasonal nature of the work, many Huffers are ready to drop everything and travel to where they’re needed. Tis freedom transfers well to the adventuring lifestyle, and also suits those seeking to return to Huffing should adventuring not supply their needs.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/huffer.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Riverfolk</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Huffer Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.YCyo4r3rZ2gMUz9Q]{Riverguide}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.R2ytluHiEFF2KQ5e]{Consume Alcohol}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Comp