e.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.IFKWu98qmWpaSfUi]{Ambidextrous}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.hTgrGkWnmIR4xhVe]{Carouser}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.r180vP86SlwyJc8W]{Criminal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.vMYEkrWj0ip6ZOdv]{Resistance (Disease)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Dose of Weirdroot, Quality Clothing<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.BLHdxZVBGTrrGdxO]{Procurer}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bSWoV1IiS5qWNw39]{Evaluate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.2LDCVJQWkTFszMok]{Lore (Law)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.epPBu7x6BRWp2PHG]{Dealmaker}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.HIofcsDLjXGKzSZf]{Embezzle}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.LPgjE0cexTVOBVCY]{Suave}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: A Ring of Hustlers<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.Q1sXSEtjvMVxd5xi]{Ringleader}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DiP9cmbqUir3HkkK]{Lore (Heraldry)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.34EBUkHQkrqF1sq7]{Briber}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.RbnrfHf7GSQap0ig]{Kingpin}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.5QcrpLQWWrsbKR79]{Numismatics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QsrXxGZiHjth7RMg]{Savvy}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Townhouse with Discreet Back Entrance, a Ring of Bawds<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"WmXiUhsOHIJia8OM","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":1100000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Herbalist","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>‘This is beyond my skill to heal. The wound’s been infected and it’s tainting his blood; he needs a doctor, or Shallya’s aid. I can give you something to make sure he’s comfortable on the journey to town. And something for you, too, to calm your nerves.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Kurtis Schwarz, Herbalist</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>Skilled botanists who use Rhya’s bounty to create cures for many ailments.</em></p><p>Medicines from apothecaries are expensive and rarely available in the Reikland’s hinterlands, so peasants rely on the healing power of plants gathered, doctored, and administered by Herbalists. Most Herbalists’ lore is verbally passed down from master to apprentice, so names for illnesses and treatments often vary from village to village. The most experienced Herbwises are sent for in cases of mysterious or stubborn sicknesses. Herbalists dedicate time to visiting the sick, diagnosing their ailments and searching for herbs to treat them with. Some Herbalists ply a darker trade, sought out by those who can pay a high price for the illicit substances they offer. Although an untrue stereotype, it’s a standing joke in the trade that Halﬂing Herbalists are only interest in pipeweed and wyrdroot.</p><p>With knowledge of poultices and potions, Herbalists can easily find a place with a band of travelers or mercenaries. When particularly virulent diseases take hold, Herbwises often send their apprentices to far off places in search of rarer herbs, and some find themselves in all manner of unexpected trouble. The Wood Elves’ knowledge of plants and herbs is legendary. In the Grey Mountains it is said that The Goddess Shallya wandered Athel Loren to learn their lore when Ranald was dying of an affiction she could not cure. High Elves who study the art of herbalism follow Lileath the Maiden’s teachings, and it’s rumored there is an ancient elven library in Marienburg which records the medicinal use of every plant in the Old World, although no Human has yet been granted access.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/herbalist.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Halfling, High Elf, Wood Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Peasants</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Herbalist Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.1cjF3aoozvxnOMb1]{Herb Gatherer}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.4IGdIhnwTaZijzg7]{Charm Animal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.sRuMlaPU5xdIrwhd]{Climb}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Herbs)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.os4NKy5Oy6sRt1eh]{Outdoor Survival}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.hodHqFNKAmu40ajh]{Swim}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Herbalist)}</em><br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.9h82z72XGo9tfgQS]{Acute Sense (Taste)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.afREA9q7v4Scuozn]{Orientation}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.q58lK4kULJZB5GjE]{Rover}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.1dUizIgLBgn4jICC]{Strider (any)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Boots, Cloak, Sling Bag containing Assortment of Herbs<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.UPF7jOq9bqc6ABgb]{Herbalist}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.R2ytluHiEFF2KQ5e]{Consume Alcohol}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pKLMbmG3Ivt6mzMf]{Haggle}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.HXZaV1CJhmTvcAz4]{Heal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.epPBu7x6BRWp2PHG]{Dealmaker}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.7bZjB82f6LSkeczP]{Nimble Fingered}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.oQzTJEXUx28sCiH3]{Sharp}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.qZ4cFy6z482ZONuA]{Sturdy}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Hand Weapon (Sickle), Healing Poultice, Trade Tools (Herbalist)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.eBirX8K2qBxdOB45]{Herb Master}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Medicine)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Poisons)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GRRN3XAKIpEVCY7z]{Craftsman (Herbalist)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.fEFAMNqh8nJIfBkM]{Field Dressing}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.zImcTgEl2XNnbu5W]{Hardy}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QsrXxGZiHjth7RMg]{Savvy}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Herb Gatherer, 3 Healing Poultices, Healing Draught, Workshop (Herbalist)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.un8r6R9QLrACK2pv]{Herbwise}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.iYan4z52v7HYM9u9]{Drive}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.zZUX7wO4rOo8k9F0]{Navigation}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wXcJWxJdw0ib5b8W]{Concoct}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GHmXS9zGNx3PWYZc]{Master Tradesman (Herbalist)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.vMYEkrWj0ip6ZOdv]{Resistance (Poison)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.580fwhKfOZJFxMID]{Savant (Herbs)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Pony and Cart<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"fTqkgehpmxk7kVT6","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":3600000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Physician","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><p>‘Come to Neuber for all your limb removals! I’ll ‘ave your arm off in seconds! I’ll suture it a’fore you even wake up. My work’s so fine you’ll never miss it!’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Gotthard Neuber, Barber-Surgeon</em></p><p>‘Beware the Brass Doktor.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Reikland Proverb warning against cheap Physicians</em></p><p>‘They’re bastards, all. I can’t so much as give you a proper bloodletting without their leave. “Practicing medicine without a license” my arse. I know you can’t afford them, deary. Here, luv, take this nice tea. What? Oh no, just tea is all. Just tea. And if you feel better, why, thank Shallya, eh?’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Jana Palner, Part-time Surgeon</em></p></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>With a strong stomach and steady hand, you practice the art of medicine, striving to save lives.</em></p><p>Physicians study patients’ symptoms and prescribe remedies and surgeries. While the healing arts are ancient, many deriving from Elven practices, the formal science of medicine is relatively new and not-entirely-trusted. Due to the Empire’s history with necromancy and the safe-guards imposed by the Cult of Morr, studying cadavers is forbidden, making learning of anatomy hard. Medicine’s reputation suffered further from swindlers selling ‘miracle cure-alls’ that do nothing or cause actual harm. Physicians learn their profession at a university or while apprenticed to a Guild Physician. Most cheap surgery is undertaken by back-street physicians known as barber-surgeons whose training is informal. Trained doctors with strong stomachs are in demand for the State Armies. The most famed Physicians almost exclusively tend to wealthy merchants and the nobility.</p><p>Physician’s Guild fees are notoriously expensive, which can cause newer Physicians without steady clientele to seek alternate sources of income. Some Physicians consistently search for more effective treatments and new medicines, which can take them far afield. Others like to expand their knowledge of anatomy by studying grievous wounds first hand, and there are few better ways to do that than by travelling with adventurers.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/physician.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling, High Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Academics</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Physician Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.qwNXUbgbXcegmh8l]{Physician's Apprentice}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d3VZwO4Y5JH5DXd