97InIX29nzgW1]{Pilot}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.4wnQc19allWlyOGe]{Strong Swimmer}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: River Runner, Speedy Riverboat<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.XCfd7wimn69mZW9T]{Smuggler King}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.RbnrfHf7GSQap0ig]{Kingpin}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QsrXxGZiHjth7RMg]{Savvy}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.1dUizIgLBgn4jICC]{Strider (Coastal)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Ij9N3G8jzxb4lrwy]{Sea Legs}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Disguise Kit, Small Fleet of Riverboats<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"FqhOxcvai4ROvhXB","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":7000000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Thief","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><p>‘One creaky ﬂoorboard in the whole place and I’m the one to find it…’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-eis.eisactors.2vtOixDMZLdjBsfl]{Alette Zimmermann}, Thief, Jailed</em></p><p>‘What the...? Those aren’t dogs... they’re bears!’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Marx the Mauled, Unlucky Thief</em></p><p>‘No, the list of charges does not include, “Stealing the magistrate’s heart away.” You must have me confused with a magistrate who has a heart.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Leonora Nithardt, Magistrate</em></p></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You steal from others in order to line your own pockets, and you’re rather good at it</em></p><p>Thieves steal all manner of wealth and goods from their fellow man. From the lowliest footpad to the wiliest burglar, the thought of an honest day’s work in return for a respectable wage is little more than a bad joke. Thieves often organize themselves into gangs alongside charlatans, racketeers, and fences to further their mutual wealth. Bitter feuds between such illicit organizations have been known to last for years or even decades. The lowliest Thieves target individuals, picking pockets or waylaying victims in rat-infested alleyways. Burglars avoid confrontation breaking into businesses and residences, carrying off portable valuables. More ambitious thieves scope out their targets for days or weeks, even going so far as to infiltrate their target locations to get a more precise lay of the land. Working with other professional burglars, such experts can organize heists of which their lesser peers can only dream.</p><p>Thieves who run afoul of the law are obliged to hide or ﬂee from justice, putting many would-be inmates on the run. Sometimes the very items stolen by Thieves are of such exorbitant value or supernatural quality they seem to attract trouble like a moldering corpse draws ﬂies, which can lead them into all sorts of unexpected adventures. Of course, a Burglar’s talents are always valuable to adventurers, and reliable examples can expect to be well-compensated for their skills.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/thief.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Rogues</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Thief Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.Ahe89KQIXpeadscI]{Prowler}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.sRuMlaPU5xdIrwhd]{Climb}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.zkI6tIqbyAZvh0Th]{Stealth (Urban)}</em><br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wBhPFggGqIXwbx1r]{Alley Cat}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.r180vP86SlwyJc8W]{Criminal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jrFIFLhyOYwcyMUl]{Flee!}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jt0DmVK9IiF6Sd2h]{Strike to Stun}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Crowbar, Leather Jerkin, Sack<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.KEEmMZK5mpcoRU69]{Thief}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bSWoV1IiS5qWNw39]{Evaluate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.AkjRsazdAppqveZu]{Pick Lock}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.AIueed3kikw3euvn]{Secret Signs (Thief)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.rvd0S8Z0v2m0MHmD]{Sleight of Hand}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wrpVYmdiIy1jPulc]{Break and Enter}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Criminals)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.9sMAf0xmehjEmUao]{Fast Hands}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.XSb3QVB9ipPBFt56]{Shadow}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Trade Tools (Thief), Rope<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.4xxp72XMEqj6y25g]{Master Thief}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d3VZwO4Y5JH5DXdT]{Bribery}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.7pQo66cESWttzIlb]{Gamble}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.OuDdJRDo3W56zk0Z]{Ranged (Crossbow)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.x0WMGwuQzReXcQrs]{Night Vision}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.7bZjB82f6LSkeczP]{Nimble Fingered}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.HpGjzrSR4tdogJtl]{Step Aside}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.a7v422EZcOUUC20X]{Trapper}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Crossbow Pistol with 10 Bolts<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.s9BcRjM1u2nE0JRD]{Cat Burglar}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.HngrTVqKis08Nvcf]{Set Trap}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.g4Q6AtzZuo5iIvD4]{Catfall}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.MGEPI4jNhymNIRVz]{Scale Sheer Surface}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.CV9btQn09S9Fn8Jk]{Strong Legs}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.OROfMcVqRnZHINkU]{Wealthy}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Dark Clothing, Grappling Hook, Mask or Scarves<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"mBtIPoWNpXwAS5Yl","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":7400000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Watchman","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>'So I go up to Middenheim, Ulric’s own country, and what did I find? I swear more than half of their City Watch are women! I would have stayed up there for the rest of my career if I could’ve.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Jana Tennisohn, Chief Inspektor (retired), Nuln City Watch</em></p><p> </p><p>‘Sorry, sir, I’ve got a Halﬂing killer, a Weirdroot smuggling ring, a gang war, and a noble threatening to have me arrested by my own Station. Your missing cat will have to wait until tomorrow.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Sergeant Harri Makkenpieser, Altdorf City Watch</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You maintain the peace and keep the rabble in line so your town doesn’t descend into anarchy.</em></p><p>Watchmen are employed by local authorities to patrol streets throughout the Empire. Most are little more than well-meaning keepers of the peace, and few know the laws they’re supposed to enforce. Corruption is rampant, and many Watchmen enlist purely for the authority to hurt people or to support local criminal gangs. Some can earn triple their wages by turning a blind eye.</p><p>Only a few towns and cities have professional Watchmen paid to understand and uphold the law; instead, the Emperor’s Peace is normally maintained by the local State Army, who man walls, guard gates, and patrol the streets according to the instructions of their superiors.</p><p>Not every Watchman is crooked, but those with morals are soon jaded by the corruption inherent in the system. By joining adventuring parties, principled Watchmen can champion justice on their own terms. Experience of the street makes Watchmen effective combatants in a small party, and their presence can help legitimize a wandering band of ne’er-do-wells.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/watchman.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling, High Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Burgher</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Watchman Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.C8pqV1AJgqS6vUd6]{Watch Recruit}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.sRuMlaPU5xdIrwhd]{Climb}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.R2ytluHiEFF2KQ5e]{Consume Alcohol}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.7pQo66cESWttzIlb]{Gamble}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.F8NfBZdVSEIGCMtu]{Melee (Any)}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}</em><br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.J9MK0AIaTbvd5oF6]{Drilled}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.zImcTgEl2XNnbu5W]{Hardy}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jt0DmVK9IiF6Sd2h]{Strike to Stun}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jviOQmy0luQOySC2]{Tenacious}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Hand Weapon, Leather Jack, Uniform<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.LobXt1Wa3x3EogpB]{Watchman}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wrpVYmdiIy1jPulc]{Break and Enter}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.r180vP86SlwyJc8W