4e-core.talents.Z91GFaT6FhEwyESU]{Tunnel Rat}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Hand Weapon (Pick), Horse and Cart, Leather Jack, Rope, Trade Tools (Thief)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.ufAAH4fyE4qfkH2c]{Treasure Hunter}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.zZUX7wO4rOo8k9F0]{Navigation}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Engineer)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.8pVzgPkgWpTJvfhG]{Fearless (Undead)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.mNoCuaVbFBflfO6X]{Sixth Sense}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Ywo6fZNPC4zbHHSQ]{Strong-minded}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.a7v422EZcOUUC20X]{Trapper}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Bedroll, Maps, Tent, Trade Tools (Engineer), Writing Kit</p>","markdown":""},"_id":"bDoNOzzUiMdKqpps","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":3000000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Bailiff","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>Aye, it’s been a poor harvest, but dues are dues. I’ll take half now and half on Marktag. How’s that? It’s the best I can offer, can’t say fairer than that.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Lena Sauer, Bailiff</em></p><p> </p><p>‘I’ll go up and have a look at the grazing land in question myself. Until then, I want no trouble from any of your boisterous offspring, do I make myself clear, Bauer, Meier? And you will pay equal shares for the damage to the inn, or you will forfeit any claim you might, or might not have, on the land.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Lorenz Schulte, Reeve of Elster Vale</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You are a local official trusted by local rulers to administer their lands efficiently and firmly</em></p><p> Nobles entrust Bailiffs to gather dues from their lands. Some Bailiffs are respected and upstanding, attending throng at the temple of Sigmar every week. Others are bullies, happy to enforce their lord’s rights over property and possessions with threats and violence. Long-serving bailiffs often become trusted servants of the local noble family and enjoy considerable perks. Reeves have a broader reach and greater responsibility. They keep order and maintain the borders of the lord’s lands, resolving disputes with neighboring estates.</p><p> Some magistrates are lay-members of the cult of Verena, seeking guidance and wisdom from blind Justice on any difficult cases they judge. However, most provincial magistrates simply find themselves arbitrating a series of petty disputes over livestock and farmland borders.</p><p> Most Bailiffs have a degree of autonomy, granting them ample opportunity to turn their attention to private matters, or to hire others to do so on their behalf. As many also have broad authority in the areas they inﬂuence, they are frequently sent by their employers to resolve problems, which can often lead to unexpected places.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/bailiff.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Peasants</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Bailiff Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.kOmgIJIYcylhEUWK]{Tax Collector}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.1jCxbFAUuFuAPLJl]{Dodge}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pKLMbmG3Ivt6mzMf]{Haggle}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.I0yPc4PH5erWJLmu]{Intimidate}</em>, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.rOPmyLWa37e7s9v6]{Melee (Basic)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.HIofcsDLjXGKzSZf]{Embezzle}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.5QcrpLQWWrsbKR79]{Numismatics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.FF41XPboORgyDNsv]{Strong Back}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jviOQmy0luQOySC2]{Tenacious}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Hand weapon, small lock box<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.9UWoLPwYyPV2TRnz]{Bailiff}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d3VZwO4Y5JH5DXdT]{Bribery}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bSWoV1IiS5qWNw39]{Evaluate}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wrpVYmdiIy1jPulc]{Break and Enter}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.r180vP86SlwyJc8W]{Criminal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.XU7D9CCmumuhqDUi]{Public Speaker}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jt0DmVK9IiF6Sd2h]{Strike to Stun}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Leather Jack, 3 Tax Collectors<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.albRTMyj0Fsr2u6A]{Reeve}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.MXy22hFCgntdlQrn]{Animal Care}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DiP9cmbqUir3HkkK]{Lore (Heraldry)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.zZUX7wO4rOo8k9F0]{Navigation}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oSbEE6eXH1S3LfUU]{Ride (Horse)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.RbnrfHf7GSQap0ig]{Kingpin}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.0hn6UaKq8CoZP2zD]{Menacing}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.AcnFuDKRemLI9ey7]{Nose for Trouble}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GogGbYxkVdCmiKqf]{Read/Write}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Horse with Saddle and Tack, Breastplate, Baili?<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.USvstPFloo15DIJ1]{Magistrate}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.61L9aX2z164cjm7K]{Language (Classical)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.2LDCVJQWkTFszMok]{Lore (Law)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.x8g3U68oi8XzWiYr]{Commanding Presence}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.mgeiaDZXei7JBEgo]{Iron Will}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QsrXxGZiHjth7RMg]{Savvy}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.b4x1qEWcevX7xK58]{Schemer}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Library (Law), Quality Robes, Seal of Office<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"UhdhIWaofKgwFKEr","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":1000000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Scout","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>‘You don’t want to be going off the road down by the bluff without a guide. Tehre’s man-traps in them woods what the reeve put down to catch poachers. Almost ‘ad old Billi’s leg off last week it did.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Gwyn, Scout</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>Intrepid and resourceful, you guide others through the dangerous wilds of the Old World.</em></p><p>Among an illiterate populace where maps are rare, local knowledge can mean the difference between life and death for travelers. Scouts are experts at finding safe paths through the backwoods and muddy roads of the Empire. Local guides will accompany their clients, warning of upcoming dangers, sharing village gossip or showing the best places to forage. Experienced Scouts will barely be seen by their employers as they explore the trails ahead and keep a watchful eye out for hidden dangers. While most Scouts keep to familiar territory, some specialize in safely navigating unmapped terrain. Explorers might venture even further into treacherous and hostile territory, filling in the blank spaces on their maps. Most Scouts do not tackle dangers themselves, preferring to slip away quietly to warn their companions and enable their employers to avoid potential hazards completely.</p><p>Scouts can be invaluable to a group of adventurers, especially those venturing out from a city for the first time to find their fortune. Reliable and knowledgeable Guides may find themselves asked to stay on and act as Scouts, although many still act the loner, slipping in and out of the woods to protect the group from ambush or warn of enemies ahead.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/scout.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling, High Elf, Wood Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Peasants</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Scout Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.D8Bx5CgvvMpIkwSq]{Guide}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.4IGdIhnwTaZijzg7]{Charm Animal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.sRuMlaPU5xdIrwhd]{Climb}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.rOPmyLWa37e7s9v6]{Melee (Basic)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.os4NKy5Oy6sRt1eh]{Outdoor Survival}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}</em><br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.afREA9q7v4Scuozn]{Orientation}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.q58lK4kULJZB5GjE]{Rover}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.oQzTJEXUx28sCiH3]{Sharp}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.1dUizIgLBgn4jICC]{Strider (any)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Hand Weapon, Leather Jack, Sturdy Boots and Cloak, Rope<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.4bCFwNAaudD9wb40]{Scout}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.zZUX7wO4rOo8k9F0]{Navigation}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.ZQSm2AwrgT2cHG0C]{Ranged (Bow)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oSbEE6eXH1S3LfUU]{Ride (Horse)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Xk5tp3aasPNtk4zt]{Stealth (Rural)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.rt2rGSwFDCDHPh0A]{Track}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.0LdHytqyNmg2pcAX]{Combat Aware}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.x0WMGwuQzReXcQrs]{Night Vision}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.AcnFuDKRemLI9ey7]{Nose for Trouble}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jQmIu8P85tF0njmD]{Seasoned Traveller}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Bow and 10 Arrows, Mail Shirt<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.nCijLyJxZ8UfeNfV]{Pathfinder}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.MXy22hFCgntdlQrn]{Animal Care}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pKLMbmG3Ivt6mzMf]{Haggle}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bVdhLdfuSAfMi3qq]{Secret Signs (Hunter)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.hodHqFNKAmu40ajh]{Swim}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.9h82z72XGo9tfgQS]{Acute Sense (Sight)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.mNoCuaVbFBflfO6X]{Sixth Sense}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.CV9btQn09S9Fn8Jk]{Strong Legs}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.RmY0CUjiFYZ3GEKY]{Very Resilient}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Map, Riding Horse with Saddle and Tack, Saddlebags with 2 weeks' Rations, Tent<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.RGrmA9jAFzrR5tH5]{Explorer}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Cartographer)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.zImcTgEl2XNnbu5W]{Hardy}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.726gbrANZt8OqXr5]{Linguistics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.580fwhKfOZJFxMID]{Savant (Local)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jviOQmy0luQOySC2]{Tenacious}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Selection of Maps, Trade Tools (Cartographer)<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"HSoeyY2cbQAndBFk","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":6500000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Warden","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>‘Yes, m’lord, the duke has been a-bed this last decade. And, yes, m’lord, I am running his estate. No, m’lord, I don’t see that changing any time soon. After all, in Penzkirchen, my word is now law… Arrest him!’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– W. Edvart Kurtz, Governor of Penzkirchen</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You oversee another’s territory, ensuring it is properly maintained and, if necessary, protected</em></p><p>Wardens see to the care and stewardship of their employer’s holdings. Failure to improve — or, at the very least, maintain — an employer’s lands or provisions is often met with disfavor. In some instances, multiple wardens work together to keep their employer’s estate in correct order. A Warden’s oversight can cover a variety of duties: ensuring the upkeep of a grand estate, overseeing a lord’s hunting grounds, or caring for a rarely-visited holidaying home. Wardens might keep watch over forested or agricultural lands, or see to the maintenance of lakes, rivers, or ponds. Those in the employ of the richest and most powerful can rise to immensely powerful positions themselves.</p><p>Wardens rarely travel unless their duties call for it. That said, even those assigned to oversee an estate’s lands or hunting grounds must make regular patrols to assess the property’s condition and to discourage poachers. When between jobs, Wardens often find work as guides or hunters, and such activities can lead to much excitement or terror. Wardens with a grudge against former masters might even be inclined to provide enemies with confidential information regarding their old estates.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/warden.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling, High Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Courtier</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Warden Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.WvEHWvF7hoyNChqj]{Custodian}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.LGHozP5gmQ8cuDQV]{Athletics}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.4IGdIhnwTaZijzg7]{Charm Animal}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.R2ytluHiEFF2KQ5e]{Consume Alcohol}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.cYtU0ORRFCOpQLWz]{Intuition}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}</em><br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talent