e.careers.pru2uoIq7hM13pYm]{Entertainer}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.0CwV96kTDRF0jUhk]{Entertain (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.MeXCAQ3wqJzX07X7]{Ride (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.rOPmyLWa37e7s9v6]{Melee (Basic)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.HO8vIjGTHjmenIaV]{Perform (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.bBLK2hznjPlby6Jb]{Play (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.NSnpJQiky8JcMnme]{Ranged (Throwing)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.TaYriYcJkFuIdBKp]{Contortionist}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.BIaLeh4CPFaTMbFz]{Jump Up}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jrYW2OyDHd1Md2my]{Sharpshooter}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.FjTnaxixsu1ShNNr]{Trick Riding}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Costume, Instrument, Selection of Scripts (that you can't yet read), Throwing Weapons<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.bNwRfl5P64gXgZON]{Troubadour}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 3<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.MXy22hFCgntdlQrn]{Animal Care}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.uZpeJ8P0g10UBRdE]{Animal Training (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.fdq3RFSOKl5b3WzW]{Art (Writing)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Any)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.77p3QRKgFWakkndF]{Blather}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.WoXShzaYkV5F6c48]{Master of Disguise}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.pQjZdMJDDaz0DpAD]{Perfect Pitch}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GogGbYxkVdCmiKqf]{Read/Write}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Trained Animal, Writing Kit<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.dNd0JKvUqjP3kiuy]{Troupe Leader}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Gold 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.epPBu7x6BRWp2PHG]{Dealmaker}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.jQmIu8P85tF0njmD]{Seasoned Traveller}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.oQzTJEXUx28sCiH3]{Sharp}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Draught Horses and Wagon (Stage), Wardrobe of Costumes and Props, Troupe of Entertainers<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"5nIDu8oyFVShLqne","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":2300000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Nun","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><p>‘They came thinking it a simple task to slay a few poor, hapless Brothers and take our relics. I ask Morr not judge too harshly the seven bandits we bury today, as Brother Hild has already inﬂicted punishment enough.’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Abbot Ernst Halfhauser</em></p><p>‘Quick! Come quick! The Sisters of Faith and Chastity are about to parade through the streets. I want to see if I can get a few coppers caught in their thorns. It brings luck for the whole year!’</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– Bengt, Altdorf Street Rat</em></p></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>You are devoted to the service of your deity, having sworn vows for a life of service.</em></p><p>Nuns are members of religious orders, normally cloistered within an abbey, convent, or monastery. Most rise before the sun for morning prayer before toiling in fields, tending to the sick, or preserving important manuscripts. Vows of pilgrimage cause some to travel the Empire, while others take oaths to serve the community, moving amongst the people, tending to their spiritual needs. Devoted hermits and tenders to shrines are also thought of as ‘Nuns’ or ‘Monks’ by the folk of the Empire. Many Nuns learn valuable trades such as vintners, brewers or calligraphers. Abbesses use these activities to attract donations and patronage from the local nobility. Leaders of particularly large or martial Orders can gather significant inﬂuence both within their own cult and with the ruling classes of a province. For more on religion and the different Orders, see Chapter 7: Religion and Belief.</p><p>When a religious order discovers terrible secrets or fragments of prophecy, its leaders may feel they must act, sending brothers and sisters abroad. Abbeys along pilgrimage routes will often also send their members abroad to guard the many pilgrims traversing the lengthy holy roads across the Empire. And there are always itinerant Friars wandering the world, risking adventure with every new land they enter.</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/nun.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Academics</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"no-toc\">Nun Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.Zst72kU4epCqabW9]{Novitiate (Nun)}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.fdq3RFSOKl5b3WzW]{Art (Calligraphy)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.pxNjTxsp1Kp0SmQe]{Cool}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.CcNJsS4jSwB6Ug1J]{Endurance}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.0CwV96kTDRF0jUhk]{Entertain (Storyteller)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.RLQHm1s4IuY9RSr2]{Gossip}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.HXZaV1CJhmTvcAz4]{Heal}, <em>@UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d9bGxy6Y3u3rOHIN]{Lore (Theology)}</em>, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9xR9uO8FIvi4YsJp]{Pray}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.QyjWtSdnVMT04l5Y]{Bless (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.spdiWsONKTzkLbg3]{Stone Soup}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.eEHauevJWhmzvCSx]{Panhandle}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.GogGbYxkVdCmiKqf]{Read/Write}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Religious Symbol, Robes<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♟ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.Lkk2NQC1dkUb6yOS]{Nun}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Brass 4<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.F8NfBZdVSEIGCMtu]{Melee (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.9tbHTeuvEMZrp0rx]{Research}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Brewer)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Herbalist)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.wKwel9MG7NIG3i3w]{Trade (Vintner)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.sYbgpSnRqSZWgwFP]{Etiquette (Cultists)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.fEFAMNqh8nJIfBkM]{Field Dressing}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Nj3tC8A5fZ3zEdMR]{Holy Visions}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.voV0C2ar1bKpcpnH]{Invoke (Any)}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Book (Religion), Religious Relic, Trade Tools (Any)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♜ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.TDErU66ZoIirO2dF]{Abbess}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 2<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.oMaJZ5cvCJeOUq9H]{Leadership}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Local)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Politics)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.Fs06sr7y9JKpVQmB]{Perception}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.vMYEkrWj0ip6ZOdv]{Resistance (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.nWLsoWQBCjPRKxYx]{Robust}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.580fwhKfOZJFxMID]{Savant (Theology)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.IogM5gnsoOX63w7j]{Stout-hearted}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Abbey, Library (Theology)<br /><br /></p><h3><strong>♛ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.qG1ICjU4hcAhrpmW]{Prioress General}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 5<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Any)}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Any)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.x8g3U68oi8XzWiYr]{Commanding Presence}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.mgeiaDZXei7JBEgo]{Iron Will}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.wNvPXAhlKABl6hpk]{Pure Soul}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.talents.Ywo6fZNPC4zbHHSQ]{Strong-minded}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Religious Order<br /><br /></p>","markdown":""},"_id":"f5m7s9K2y1zQNmej","image":{},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"sort":5000000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{"core":{}}},{"name":"Bounty Hunter","type":"text","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<blockquote><div><div><div><p>‘It’s amazing just how many boys will wrap themselves in manacles if you smile sweetly enough. And if that doesn’t work, it’s out with the knives!</p><p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>– @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-eis.eisactors.cmLwczXnX2dsUWj0]{Anke Dorﬂinger}, Bounty Hunter</em></p></div></div></div></blockquote><p> </p><div><div><div><p><em>Ruthless and determined, you pursue your quarry to the bitter end: for justice, or for money.</em></p><p>Bounty Hunters track down fugitives and outlaws for coin. Most are legally appointed by provincial courts and receive warrant papers granting license to seize or sometimes kill the target. While some are motivated by Verena’s justice, most are more concerned by the rewards, often finding the ‘dead’ in ‘dead or alive’ to be the most convenient route to their fortune. Many Bounty Hunters start as Thief-Takers, those hired by crime victims to retrieve stolen goods. Over time, those with an established reputation may find permanent work from a merchant or noble house, guild, or cult, or may build a company of Bounty Hunters, working as a group to collect the largest rewards.</p><p>In their pursuit of wanted criminals, Bounty Hunters often stumble into unplanned adventures. As independent operatives, Bounty Hunters are perfectly suited to dropping their day job to pursue whatever business is afoot. Further, given their broad base of skills are always in demand, it is not uncommon to see Bounty Hunters turning their hand to adventuring full-time, hiring their skills out in return for payments. Bounty Hunters are a perfect starting career as they present a solid mixture of social and combat skills allowing you to contribute no matter the circumstances</p></div></div></div><p> </p><div class=\"journal-image centered\"><img src=\"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/bounty-hunter.webp\" /></div><p><strong>Species: </strong>Human, Dwarf, Halfling, High Elf, Wood Elf</p><p><strong>Class: </strong>Ranger</p><h3 style=\"text-align:center\">Bounty Hunter Advance Scheme</h3><table style=\"height:34px\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">WS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">BS</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">S</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">T</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">I</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Agi</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Dex</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Int</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">WP</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">Fel</td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">♟</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:60px;text-align:center\">♜</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">✠</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\">♛</td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"height:17px;width:61px;text-align:center\"> </td></tr></tbody></table><h3><strong>✠ @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.careers.t1TD7YCRFbjiicvi]{Thief-taker}</strong></h3><p><strong>Status</strong>: Silver 1<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.d3VZwO4Y5JH5DXdT]{Bribery}, @UUID[Compendium.wfrp4e-core.skills.exLrBrn2mjb6x2Cq]{Charm}, @UUID[Compe